Thanks for the download but it seems there is a problem with the audio. I tried VLC and mplayer, the same, almost no sound at low pitch ... Did anyone else find the same?

Correction: Using the latest version of VLC the sound is just fine! But be warned if you have Mac OS X 10.4.* or earlier versions, you may not be able to reproduce this 3-channel audio properly. Thanks again for this interesting upload.
